{"tid":386829,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【聲援良心犯】在囚抗爭者支援基金成立 吳靄儀任信託人之一","createTime":"2017-09-04T07:46:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T15:20:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2e27ea68f4592063a403ff93d8d13b6b662c5f6","tid":386829,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:46:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57167297&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170904\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57167297%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170904&d=yi%2F7EqKC%2F1bKY62EeZaE8pzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=234d3a5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57167297%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170904&h=dfe35d6b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57167297&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170904</a><br />\n<br />\n【聲援良心犯】在囚抗爭者支援基金成立 吳靄儀任信託人之一<br />\n<br />\n即時要聞  2017-09-04 13:50:20 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170904/large/1504504283_5567.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170904%2Flarge%2F1504504283_5567.jpg&h=6fc70fbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n數以萬計港人上月20日逼爆灣仔，聲援重奪公民廣場案、反東北案等被政府窮追猛打下淪為階下囚的16名人士，用行動告訴「政府良心犯」，他們從不孤單。主辦單位當日指參與遊行人數遠超預期，是自傘運後最多港人出席的遊行集會。社民連、香港眾志、大專政關、東北支援組當日收到市民約253萬元捐款，為妥善安排運用捐款，決成立「在囚抗爭者支援基金」，4個團體同意上述遊行所籌得之款項全數撥捐本基金，作為首筆捐款。<br />\n<br />\n3名基金信託人為前立法會議員吳靄儀、嶺南大學文化研究系副教授許寶強、杜耀明。基金會用於在囚者日用品物資、法律費用、親友探監交通費及定額支援金等。捐款戶口(香港職工會聯盟戶口)︰恆生銀行︰295-164578-009，戶口英文名：Hong Kong Confederation of Trade Unions。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t【聲援良心犯】沈祖堯最後一次主持開學禮：信法官憑專業態度判決<br />\n即時要聞 1小時前<br />\n\t【聲援良心犯】東北案判詞拖逾半月未出礙上訴 長毛：唔識寫？<br />\n即時要聞 25分鐘前<br />\n\t【聲援良心犯】中大生用政治犯名單布圍民女像 批沈祖堯政治保守<br />\n即時要聞 1小時前<br />\n\t趁開學禮「贈慶」 中大多處現大量港獨告示及巨型直幡<br />\n即時要聞 1小時前<br />\n\t【聲援良心犯】葉寶琳：大陸式法治檢控 支持者過百封信寄獄中<br />\n即時要聞 14小時前"},{"pid":"4aac4a919fe60d00ac733a73a38f6718efad1783","tid":386829,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bebd8fe91da06fb07fe5b3f43d99042f21bb14f1","tid":386829,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:55:50.000Z","msg":"一定支持"},{"pid":"d68bfeff4f2e1471ebfb723ee67378bc3541dbe1","tid":386829,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:23:46.000Z","msg":"之前中學去立法會類似訪問過佢，真係有識之士，講野有紋有路，可惜冇再選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fdc3ed0c3893b5b148b160d496f1f9f38a83e8c","tid":386829,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T12:30:55.000Z","msg":"在囚抗爭者支援基金<br />\n<br />\n恆生銀行︰295-164578-009<br />\n<br />\n戶口英文名：Hong Kong Confederation of Trade Unions"},{"pid":"7a432011b333de49f00b66f682def9074e8a14b4","tid":386829,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T15:20:57.000Z","msg":"共特"}]}